        u: `<span style='color:#ffcb4a'>　<br /></span><span style='color:#ffffff'>Every </span><span style='color:#11ff11'>Elemental Skill</span><span style='color:#ffffff'> will have a </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>%d%%</span><span style='color:#ffffff'> chance<br />to place a </span><span style='color:#11ff11'>Bequeath</span><span style='color:#ffffff'> effect on the target.</span>`,
