        d: `Dao Đóa Ngạo Sương　<span style='color:#ffcb4a'>%s/5<br /></span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>Loneliness reflected in water, like the unyielding flower to the frost in autumn.<br /></span><span style='color:#00ffff'>Elegant Resistance+1<br />(Dispels Certain Debuffs)<br /></span><span style='color:#ffffff'>Thời gian thi triển: 2 giây<br /></span><span style='color:#11ff11'> Yêu cầu vũ khí: Quyển<br /></span><span style='color:#11aaff'>Chúc phúc quần thể</span><span style='color:#ffffff'></span>`,
        u: `<span style='color:#ffcb4a'>　<br /></span><span style='color:#ffffff'></span><span style='color:#11ff11'>*Costs </span><span style='color:#11aaff'>%d%%</span><span style='color:#ffffff'></span><span style='color:#11ff11'> of Max Spirit, the recovery effect will not go into <br />effect with insufficient spirit*</span><span style='color:#ffffff'>　　　　　　　　　<br /></span><span style='color:#ffffff'>Instantly restores an amount of Health to teammates within </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>%d</span><span style='color:#ffffff'> meters of the caster equal to </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>%d</span><span style='color:#ffffff'> Health.<br />For the next </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>12</span><span style='color:#ffffff'> giây, each giây will restore Health equal to </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>%.1f%%</span><span style='color:#ffffff'> of Max Spirit plus<br />Max Attack Power multiplied by </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>%.1f</span><span style='color:#ffffff'>. Thời gian hồi kỹ năng: </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>75</span><span style='color:#ffffff'> giây.<br /></span><span style='color:#00ffff'>*Healing has a </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>8%%</span><span style='color:#00ffff'> chance to trigger an Extreme Healing effect, each Extreme Healing<br />will have a </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>%d%%</span><span style='color:#00ffff'> chance to remove </span><span style='color:#11ff11'>Silence</span><span style='color:#00ffff'>, </span><span style='color:#11ff11'>Paralyze</span><span style='color:#00ffff'>, </span><span style='color:#11ff11'>Sleep</span><span style='color:#00ffff'>, <br /></span><span style='color:#11ff11'>Taunt</span><span style='color:#00ffff'>, </span><span style='color:#11ff11'>Freeze</span><span style='color:#00ffff'>, </span><span style='color:#11ff11'>Fear</span><span style='color:#00ffff'>, </span><span style='color:#11ff11'>Change Yin to Yang</span><span style='color:#00ffff'> from teammates*</span><span style='color:#ffffff'></span>`,
