        u: `<span style='color:#ffcb4a'>　</span><span style='color:#ffffff'><br /></span><span style='color:#11aaff'>%d chân khí </span><span style='color:#ffffff'><br />Attack a target </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>3</span><span style='color:#ffffff'> times, dealing extra damage equal to </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>%d%%</span><span style='color:#ffffff'> of Attack Power <br />plus </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>%d</span><span style='color:#ffffff'>. Skill hits with an additional </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>5%%</span><span style='color:#ffffff'> of Critstrike Rate. <br />Thời gian hồi kỹ năng: </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>6</span><span style='color:#ffffff'> giây.<br /></span><span style='color:#aaffff'>* Bodhimanda+2 Every </span><span style='color:#11ff11'>20</span><span style='color:#aaffff'> caster's levels<br />will raise damage done to non-player targets equal to </span><span style='color:#11ff11'>2%%</span><span style='color:#aaffff'> of Attack Power</span><span style='color:#ffffff'></span>`,
